guild that *gets along*, that sucessfully completes tasks which aid each and every member within the guild, that raids often and is willing to put the time, and the loss of many wizzards live's on the line(lol).  I am real life friends with Valedar, and very good in-game friends with Dreemara.  Both members have nothing but excellent things to say about HOS.  Another reason I'd like to join is that there are many parts of the game I can no longer play by myself, I need a guild, a family to conquer parts of Everquest with.<br><br>I consider myself an experienced Everquest player.  As a few of my friends know, this is not my first character ;-)  I played another necro to the 55th level on this server, and a cleric on another.    <br><br>My guild experience on this server is as folows:<br>Level 20-50 Clan Seventh Hammer.  Led by Gervain, was one of the best experiences ever.  The players were fun to talk to and level up with.  I was saddened by it's break up but it was to be expected with everyone leaving for bigger better things.<br>Level 50-53 Dragon Society.  It was a mighty guild led by Invictus, however, after only a week of being a member it self-destructed and temporarily disbanded. <br>Level 53-55 Forsaken Guardians.  Forsaken Guardians was a spinoff of Eastern Faith, led by Vigil.  I ran the website for Forsaken Guardians, and it was a decent one, but nobody in the guild had any dedication.  So hits were at a minimum.  Communication within the guild and lack of dedication drove myself and many others insane until it too, disbanded.<br><br>While I am only experienced to the 52nd season, I plan to level rapidly.  Especially because I believe Planes of Power will be a 60+ game... and I want IN!<br><br>I realize that this site is no longer updated, however I was told the boards are still active, as they seem.  I consider this my application, while I realize that I will need to level up before being apart of HOS.  I just hope that I can continue to group, and destroy mobs such as we did last night often, and eventually fill that Necromancer wanted spot on your forum.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uteiamat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teiamat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Shadow</span><br>  Posts: 130<br> <font color=#8B0000>(3/26/02 5:01:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=183.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Aplication and stuff </span><hr size=1> for an app send an email to <br><br>  hordeofshadows@yahoo.com<br><br> -Teiamat S'Vaan<br><br><br> PS-I am not part of High Council, but...just trying to help by posting how to get an app. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uvallerdraken.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Val Lerdraken</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#8B0000>(3/27/02 3:35:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=183.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Aplication and stuff </span><hr size=1> Hey this guy is my RL friend and he rocks! Hes been in this game longer than i have and i know hes got exp and knows his role! Even though i own him still! hehe We should really look into getting this necor guilded with us =) I mean At most times we only really have 2 necros on everyday 1 more couldnt hurt. Clerics come on i know you wants his mana lol But seriously hes a great guy and hell go anywhere and